ss=\"hkgmoji\" />CQC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n車牌有無人考？</blockquote><br />\n哩家夠有槍牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家槍牌係考左都唔可以拎返屋企<br />\n變相只可以做玩具，無左最重要既自衛功能<br />\n你不如做下research先反啦</blockquote><br />\n都係嗰句 冇撚過槍更係覺得易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自衛術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自殺術我就見得多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現行噉撚多種自衛同求生能力<br />\n有幾多香港人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只係講緊操作問題<br />\n唔係反對緊樣野<br />\n只要考牌果陣要識你講既野你已經等同反對空氣<br />\n<br />\n如果枝槍係咁無用，香港差佬一早唔再配槍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n槍唔係你講嘅情況用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可行性同成效咁低 我唔會話反嘅<br />\n唔會支持囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁係點用呢？</blockquote><br />\n有一定距離震懾用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知CQC嘅情況刀係好可能勁過手槍<br />\n你同南亞揪嘅時候會係咩距離</blockquote><br />\n香港差佬已經試過同南亞佬近戰果陣成功開槍擊斃佢，如果無左枝槍個差佬已經死左啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果南亞佬攻擊既係你條女，你枝槍就更加有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fdae3548229bba71d893dd80476d3781d1de57","tid":405864,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:06:37.000Z","msg":"打都唔夠人打, 點保護支槍?"},{"pid":"3bf05ba87df97965166f54162fc6ca41375d3e03","tid":405864,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你唔係覺得